			<div class="content" id="post-content-2366858">
									

<p>I like this. Upvote.</p>
<p>For curiosity, why did you opt to tell us what the D-class was imprisoned for, and make it such a relatively minor offense? Grand theft auto and possession of illegal substances don't get the death penalty.</p>
<p>But then, the whole &quot;the foundation only uses people on death row for D-class&quot; thing doesn't really make sense given the vast number of D-class they need.</p>

