														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2609528">
									

<p>It would be; but for me it reads to me as if Dr Davids does actually feel rather bad for the D-class who has assisted him with considerable enthusiasm until his undeserved brain death. His request to personally euthanise him rather than just allowing his routine termination seems like an act of atonement, acknowledged by permission being given - occasionally we see this in Foundation staff, and given the terrible position they find themselves in it should not be entirely a surprise. Keeping it believable yet evident in the deadpan context of an experimental report is entirely down to the skill of the writer. +1.</p>

							</div>

								
					
